    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@mthuret this is a very valid question indeed. I failed to find a way to do that without extracting and moving the code sorting the values. I think this question is broader, because in instantsearch.js we let developers use custom sort, should we apply this one?\r\n\r\nAfter testing it seems that the order is fine when returned from Algolia because we are searching. I will put an online version to let you test.",
