    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I managed to break it (Don't get me wrong, this is awesome, I just like to break stuff).\r\n\r\nWhen the network is not reliable, slow, then some requests are cancelled and other one mades. Overall at some point you find yourself in a state that is different from the last time you went to that state.\r\n\r\nIt happens with the empty query it seems.\r\n\r\nProof and steps:\r\n\r\n![bug](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/21225269/680690b2-c2d0-11e6-8545-3bf960b2f376.gif)\r\n\r\n",
